Recursive
Acronym

In current form, inasra will help you build an acronym tree that serves as a spine for a crossword.  You will have the opportunity to recursively acronymise, and so embark on a woard and meaning adventure.
the desired funcionality will build acronyms based off relevant new articles and dictionary entries
the eventual functionality will include a client that visualizes a crossword puzzle as relephant paths are created and traversed
inasra will populate a robust crossword puzzle from the spine ctreated by the user
inasra will also prepare hyper-dimensional crosswords from aggregate user sessions

